set-key="8tpqi-0-0"><span data-text="true">podchodech, hradech</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="ah374-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="ah374-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="ah374-0-0"><span data-text="true">a automobilech. A trpělivě čekali,</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="3bof3-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="3bof3-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="3bof3-0-0"><span data-text="true">až dinosauři odejdou.</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="4pa3k-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="4pa3k-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="4pa3k-0-0">&nbsp;</span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="817j3-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="817j3-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="817j3-0-0"><span data-text="true">Richard Brautigan</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">\n<p><em>Kafkův klobouk</em></p>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="fl41l-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="fl41l-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="fl41l-0-0"><span data-text="true">S de&scaron;těm, chirurgicky</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="fjp4i-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="fjp4i-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="fjp4i-0-0"><span data-text="true">ohmat&aacute;vaj&iacute;c&iacute;m střechy,</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="c4veo-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="c4veo-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="c4veo-0-0"><span data-text="true">jedl jsem zmrzlinov&yacute; poh&aacute;r,</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="7na17-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="7na17-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="7na17-0-0"><span data-