-key="1kjeo-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="1kjeo-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="1kjeo-0-0"><span data-text="true">Allen Ginsberg</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><em>&nbsp;</em></td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="a3el4-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="a3el4-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="a3el4-0-0"><span data-text="true">Dospělost</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="cklb4-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="cklb4-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="cklb4-0-0">&nbsp;</span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="ciq88-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="ciq88-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="ciq88-0-0"><span data-text="true">Jako mlad&yacute; jsem pil pivo &amp; zvracel zelenou žluč</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="c7te5-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="c7te5-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="c7te5-0-0"><span data-text="true">Jako star&scaron;&iacute; pil v&iacute;no zvracel červenou krev</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="ehbq6-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="ehbq6-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="ehbq6-0-0"><span data-text="true">Teď zvrac&iacute;m vzduch</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="afp34-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="afp34-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="afp34-0-0">&nbsp;</span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="dhh77-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="dhh77-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="dhh77-0-0"><span data-text="true">Allen Ginsberg</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="bflo7-0-0">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="bflo7-0-0">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="2jldg-0-0">&nbsp;\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-offset-key="6613m-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" style="text-align: center;" data-offset-key="6613m-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="6613m-0-0"><span data-text="true">Vzd&aacute;len&eacute; př&iacute;telkyni</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" style="text-align: center;" data-block="true" data-offset-key="88rk4-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="88rk4-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="88rk4-0-0">&nbsp;</span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" style="text-align: center;" data-block="true" data-offset-key="1ujs7-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="1ujs7-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="1ujs7-0-0"><span data-text="true">Poněvadž jsem tě kdysi zbil,</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" style="text-align: center;" data-block="true" data-offset-key="54o8o-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="54o8o-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="54o8o-0-0"><span data-text="true">opil&yacute; a pobodan&yacute; t&yacute;dny tr&aacute;pen&iacute;,</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" style="text-align: center;" data-block="true" data-offset-key="98ipn-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="98ipn-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="98ipn-0-0"><span data-text="true">a v&iacute;c jsem tě neuviděl</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" style="text-align: center;" data-block="true" data-offset-key="6g5hk-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="6g5hk-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="6g5hk-0-0"><span data-text="true">a tys dnes pro mě měla klidn&aacute; slova,</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" style="text-align: center;" data-block="true" data-offset-key="8nlo2-0-0">\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="8nlo2-0-0"><em><span data-offset-key="8nlo2-0-0"><span data-text="true"> mysl&iacute;m si teď,</span></span></em></div>\n</div>\n<div class="" style=